{"tid":1373391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全部人入黎]以後唔準叫幾點幾點一齊走","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:59:01.000Z","uid":8954,"like":158,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"46e526b7b5a4d102058758db45c610ac9714804f","tid":1373391,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"721又話2325走<br />\n今日又話1930走<br />\n有無真係問過哂咁多條前線嘅人先傳呢個訊息呀？<br />\n發夢 每次響前線啲人都好撚心灰呀屌 <br />\n明明7點幾南邊西邊圍係無需要走<br />\n<br />\n咁多位真係驚嘅 無gear嘅手足<br />\n要走就自己走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你地真係擔心前線 <br />\n都應該係叫大家慢慢行後 <br />\n而唔係搭正幾點一定要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好騎劫前線呀唔該<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 大家加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"beddff650cc944b36f9b726718bc1da8d783285d","tid":1373391,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feb6bf2e0f497e10d36a6e596165205b162e57d","tid":1373391,"uid":35815,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7495070495d179afa73b567f6f2992e6fbdb7f93","tid":1373391,"uid":8954,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9feb6bf2e0f497e10d36a6e596165205b162e57d","tid":1373391,"uid":35815,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"我懷疑係左膠/泛民派人吹風<br />\n根本前線無人咁講<br />\n<br />\n希望大家以後見到叫人走嘅仆街<br />\n即刻罵爆佢地"},{"pid":"be8e5a3865205f51ea01065b521fa18318a639e5","tid":1373391,"uid":126283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"只准前線講幾時走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢度講當擾亂軍心處理<img src=